targets.query:
eaton_sum = from(bucket: "bucket1")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "eaton_input_power")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "inputWatts")
  |> last()
  |> drop(columns: ["agent_host"])
  |> drop(columns: ["phase"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 1m, fn: sum, createEmpty: false)

  raritan_sum = from(bucket: "bucket1")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "raritan-pdu" and r.name =~ /model\/pdu\/0-pdu-2[1-6][b,r]-eu-spdc.cisco.com/)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._field == "activePower")
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({r with _value: r._value * 1000.0}))
  |> last()
  |> drop(columns: ["name"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 1m, fn: sum, createEmpty: false)

  join(
	tables: {d1: eaton_sum, d2: raritan_sum},
    on: ["_time"]
  )
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({r with _value_d1: float(v: r._value_d1)}))
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({r with _value: r._value_d1 + r._value_d2 }))
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
    r with
        total_power: r._value,
  }))
  |> keep(columns: ["total_power"])

timeInterval = 1h

eaton_sum = from(bucket: "bucket1")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "eaton_input_power")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "inputWatts")
  |> last()
  |> drop(columns: ["agent_host"])
  |> drop(columns: ["phase"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 1m, fn: sum, createEmpty: false)
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({r with _value: float(v: r._value)}))

raritan_sum = from(bucket: "bucket1")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "raritan-pdu" and r.name =~ /model\/pdu\/0-pdu-2[1-6][b,r]-eu-spdc.cisco.com/)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._field == "activePower")
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({r with _value: r._value * 1000.0}))
  |> last()
  |> drop(columns: ["name"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 1m, fn: sum, createEmpty: false)
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({r with _value: float(v: r._value)}))

  

union = union(tables: [eaton_sum, raritan_sum])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: timeInterval, fn: sum)
  |> truncateTimeColumn(unit: timeInterval)
  |> keep(columns: ["_value", "_time"])
  |> group(columns: ["_time"])
  |> first()
  |> group()

co2eqkwh = from(bucket: "bucket1")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
      r._measurement == "electricity-map" and
      r._field == "carbonIntensity" and r.cc == "IT-CNO")
  |> drop(columns: ["_measurement"])
  |> truncateTimeColumn(unit: timeInterval)
  |> drop(columns: ["_measurement", "_stop", "_start"])
  |> window(every: timeInterval)
  |> mean()
  |> duplicate(as: "_time", column: "_start")
  |> drop(columns: ["_measurement", "_stop", "_start"])
  |> truncateTimeColumn(unit: timeInterval)
  |> group(columns: ["_time"])
  |> first()

j_co2 = join(
  tables: {t1: union, t2: co2eqkwh},
    on: ["_time"],
  )
    |> map(fn: (r) => ({
    r with
        _value: float(v: r._value_t1) * float(v: r._value_t2) / 1000.0,
  }))
    |> map(fn: (r) => ({
    r with
        total_co2: r._value,
  }))
  |> keep(columns: ["total_power"])
    |> keep(columns: ["_time", "total_co2", "cc"])
    |> group()
    |> yield()
